			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "Into the Deep"
			tasks: [{
				id: "100000000000004F"
				title: "Catch a Cobblemon underground or in a cave"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "&bCavern Crawler"
			x: 4.0d
			y: 2.0d
		}
		{
			description: [
				"High altitude is its own biome category, and Flying and Dragon types prefer the heights. Climb above Y=128 in a mountain biome and you'll find species that simply don't appear at lower elevations."
				""
				"Terralith adds towering peaks that push well above vanilla height limits — the higher you go, the rarer the spawns. Bring stamina food and a solid fall-damage plan."
				""
				"Mountain Cobblemon tend to be strong and fast. Come prepared for a challenge."
				""
				"&7Tip: Terralith adds towering peaks — the higher you go, the rarer the spawn.&r"
			]
			icon: "cobblemon:ultra_ball"
