		}
		{
			description: [
				"The &eFight or Flight Reborn&r mod adds reactive wild behaviour — some Cobblemon will flee from you if they sense danger, and others will charge in aggressively."
				""
				"Fleeing Cobblemon are a test of preparation. &eQuick Balls&r are most effective on the very first throw, so the moment a chase starts, don't hesitate — throw immediately."
				""
				"Successfully catching a fleeing Cobblemon takes quick thinking and the right ball in hand before the encounter even starts."
				""
				"&7Tip: Quick Balls are most effective on the very first turn — throw immediately when a chase starts.&r"
			]
			icon: "cobblemon:quick_ball"
			id: "1000000000000059"
			min_width: 340
			rewards: [{
