				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "square"
			subtitle: "The Hunt is On"
			tasks: [{
				id: "1000000000000057"
				title: "Catch a fleeing Cobblemon (Fight or Flight Reborn)"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "&bSteady Approach"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 4.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["1000000000000059"]
			description: [
				"Some Cobblemon won't flee — they'll charge directly at you. An aggressive wild Cobblemon initiates the battle itself, and it may have bonus stats or heightened aggression to match."
				""
				"Don't let the sudden attack catch you off guard. Keep your strongest Cobblemon at the front of your party when exploring areas with territorial species."
				""
				"Winning against an aggressive encounter earns extra XP and proves you can handle what the wild throws at you unprompted."
				""
				"&7Tip: Aggressive Cobblemon may have bonus stats — come prepared with your best team member.&r"
			]
