		{
			dependencies: ["100000000000005D"]
			description: [
				"Fight or Flight Reborn creates a living ecosystem — predator Cobblemon will actively hunt prey species in the wild, and you can watch it happen without being involved at all."
				""
				"Find a mixed-type biome where predator and prey types coexist, then observe from a distance. Watch one Cobblemon pursue another for at least 30 seconds."
				""
				"It's a reminder that this world doesn't revolve around you. It existed before you arrived and keeps going whether you're watching or not."
				""
				"&7Tip: Watch near mixed-type biomes where predator and prey types coexist naturally.&r"
			]
